title: Olay Total Effects Anti-Aging Fragrance Free Moisturizer 1.7 Fl Oz

Gentle Exfoliation: Smoothes and evens skin texture. Pore Refinement: Minimizes the appearance of pores. Free Radical Defense: Helps prevent damage to skin’s surface. Subtle Lifting: Hydrates for firmer skin appearance. Visibly younger-looking skin with an appearance that’s more resilient to aging. THIS EXCLUSIVE FORMULA IS: Color and Fragrance-Free, Dermatologically tested, Non-Comedogenic (won’t clog pores), Oil-free and Fast-Absorbing.
